==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Lucubrate
<hw>Lu"cu*brate</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To elaborate, perfect, or
compose, by night study or by laborious endeavor.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lucubration</ent>⟦br⟧
